# Types & Schemas Rule

**Consult first:** `docs/context/agents_spec.md`, `docs/context/metadata_schema.md`, `docs/context/backend_api_spec.md`.

- Implement types **exactly** as specified (`LorePack`, `ArtSet`, `VoteConfig`, `VoteResult`, `MintReceipt`, `AttestationReceipt`, `RunState`, `PreparedTx`).
- Do not rename fields or change shapes. Update imports across apps when types change.
- Provide zod or JSON Schema validators where helpful, but preserve field names and optionality.
